==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: tóng shì tiānyá lúnluò rén
===Etymology===
*From the poem: ''The Song of the [[w:Pipa|Pipa]] Player'' ([[琵琶行]]), by [[w:Bai Juyi|Bai Juyi]] (白居易)
*Literally: We are (two) people stranded (together) from the far corners of the realm.

===Proverb===
'''[[同]][[是]][[天涯]][[淪落]][[人]]'''
# Those who have the same misfortune sympathize with each other.
===Alternate forms===
[[同是天涯沦落人]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
